title: Gun shot wound victim shows up at York Hospital 19 hours ago
content: shooting-generic-jpg-3221693-ver1-0.jpg      According to York City Police around 10:00 pm a gun shot wound victim arrived via private vehicle to York Hospital.    They are in stable condition.    Anyone with any information is urged to call York City Police at 717-846-1234.
